{"id":22816,"date":"2016-07-12T13:04:40","date_gmt":"2016-07-12T18:04:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/art.2marketing.ca\/?page_id=22816"},"modified":"2024-10-22T22:31:15","modified_gmt":"2024-10-22T22:31:15","slug":"faq","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aurahairstudio.ca\/faq\/","title":{"rendered":"FAQ"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row full_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; columns_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; enable_overlay=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;innerTitleBanner&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1729636272734{background-image: url(https:\/\/aurahairstudio.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/shutterstock_1670721052.webp?id=63017) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}&#8221; overlay_bg=&#8221;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"secondFont\">FREQUENTLY ASKED<\/span><br \/>\nQUESTIONS<\/h2>\n<p>At Aura Hair Studio, we understand that choosing the right salon and service can come with a lot of questions. Whether you&#8217;re curious about our hair treatments, booking policies, or what to expect during your visit, we&#8217;re here to provide all the answers. Below are some of the most common questions we receive from our clients to help you make the most of your experience with us.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;FaqsList&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2>FAQ<\/h2>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"accordion accordion-sm accordion-title-underlined accordion-expander-lg vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" id=\"vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\"\n     role=\"tablist\" aria-multiselectable=\"true\">\n\n\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  active \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\" data-id=\"lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDo I need to book an appointment in advance at Aura Hair Salon innisfil?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721767735442-1795e3f8-74e4\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Yes, we recommend booking your appointment in advance to ensure availability, especially for popular times and special services like bridal or colour treatments.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\" data-id=\"lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHow can I book an appointment at your hair salon?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721767735459-fe8a0698-3021\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]You can easily book your appointment online through our website or by giving us a call. We\u2019re always happy to assist with your booking needs.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\" data-id=\"lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat services do you offer for women\u2019s hair?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721767735473-5e3145b2-a05f\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]We offer a wide range of services, including haircuts, colouring, blowouts, hair spa treatments, and bridal hair styling. Check out our service pages for more details.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\" data-id=\"lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDo you provide hair services for men and children?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721767735493-cd513b02-2699\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Yes, Aura Hair Studio is a unisex salon offering specialized haircuts, grooming, and styling services for men, as well as haircut and styling services for children aged 4 to 12.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\" data-id=\"lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat is the price range for your hair services?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721838489828-b5661f25-be76\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Our pricing varies depending on the service. Women\u2019s haircuts start at $68+, men\u2019s haircuts start at $25+, and children\u2019s haircuts start at $22+. We also offer premium colour and treatment services.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHow often should I get my hair cut or coloured?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839579475-be19dfe4-b3c5\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]We recommend getting a haircut every 6-8 weeks to maintain healthy hair and shape. For colour, it depends on the service\u2014typically, touch-ups are needed every 4-6 weeks for regrowth.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDo you offer bridal or event styling?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839667071-13cf61d9-c782\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Yes, at Aura Hair Studio we offer bridal styling, bridesmaid and other members of the wedding party hair, and special occasion hair services. We also provide trial runs for brides to ensure everything is perfect for your big day.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat products do you use?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839691714-d5c4c948-7d25\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]We use professional-grade products known for their quality and gentleness on hair. Our products are designed to protect and enhance your hair, ensuring long-lasting results.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839717453-2ed5146c-0e8d\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839717453-2ed5146c-0e8d\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839717453-2ed5146c-0e8d\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839717453-2ed5146c-0e8d\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839717453-2ed5146c-0e8d\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839717453-2ed5146c-0e8d\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCan I bring photos of a hairstyle I want?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n          