rent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839744617-294c083e-580f\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Yes, consultations are available for all our services, especially for complex treatments like color changes, haircuts, or wedding styling.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDo you offer hair treatments for damaged or dry hair?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839766171-db321762-569a\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Yes, we offer a range of hair spa treatments, including Olaplex, moisture treatments, and shine treatments, to revitalize and nourish damaged or dry hair.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIs eyebrow tinting available at the salon?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839815223-87ee1a00-fe85\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]Yes, we offer eyebrow tinting services to enhance your brows and give them fuller definition. It\u2019s a great addition to any hair service![\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"accordion-item panel  \">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-heading\" role=\"tab\" id=\"heading_lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\" data-id=\"lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\">\n                    <h4 class=\"accordion-title\" data-controls=\"lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                        <a tabindex=\"0\" class=\"collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"  data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\"\n                           data-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" href=\"#lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\" data-bs-target=\"#lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\"\n                           aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat is your cancellation policy?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                                <span class=\"accordion-expander\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-add\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"lqd-icn-ess icon-ion-ios-close\"><\/i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                        <\/a>\n\n                    <\/h4>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div id=\"lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\"\n                    data-bs-parent=\"#vc_accordion_69e45f3ac4e3c\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"heading_lqd-1721839835756-4821c046-b99a\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t[vc_column_text]We kindly ask that you provide at least 24 hours&#8217; notice for cancellations or rescheduling. This allows us to accommodate other clients and manage our schedule efficiently.[\/vc_column_text]                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\t\t\t            <di